thread.title_full: On President's Day, protestors gather at Rosa Parks Circle for anti-Trump rally and march

author: Dominick Mastrangelo | dmastra1@mlive.com
title: On President's Day, protestors gather at Rosa Parks Circle for anti-Trump rally and march
text: About 200 people yelled anti-Donald Trump chants, revealed apprehension about national politics and discussed initiatives to maintain a quality of life they say is under attack.
